      "page": 1,
      "title": "Back To School, Phone In Hand?",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Back To School, Phone In Hand?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<p>Back-to-school season is here. Does your child already have a phone? If not, are they about to ask for one? Here's what you need to know before you buy them a phone. Let's dive in!</p>\n<img alt=\"Back To School, Phone In Hand?_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 2,
      "title": "Back To School, Phone In Hand?",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Back To School, Phone In Hand?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. First Phone, First Lesson</h4>\n<p>Before kids use their first phone, they need to understand financial responsibility. They should know the actual monthly bill and check all data plan limits. Make them aware of hidden costs, like paid apps and fancy phone cases. Once they grasp these, they will truly understand that a phone is not a toy.</p>\n<img alt=\"Back To School, Phone In Hand?_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 3,
      "title": "Back To School, Phone In Hand?",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Back To School, Phone In Hand?</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>2. Smartphones And Smart Deals</h4>\n<p>When children get a new phone, consider having them do some chores. So they can earn pocket money to pay for their bills. Additionally, some phone plans offer special rates for students. Be sure to ask about these before signing up.</p>\n<img alt=\"Back To School, Phone In Hand?_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/back-to-school-phone-in-hand/back-to-school-phone-in-hand_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
    },
